{"tid":13754,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"召喚電結他JJ effect 火牛問題","createTime":"2016-11-30T08:08:15.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-01T07:36:59.000Z","uid":26778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8ca513df651f99d838a1430d782eb905dda84060","tid":13754,"uid":26778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T08:08:15.000Z","msg":"岩岩玩左電結冇耐 <br />\n想問下應該點樣揀power supply <br />\n之前一直用緊一條豬腸駁長果種火牛 但用落好似好多noise <br />\n<br />\n各位可唔可教下小弟點揀power supply 同埋有咩推介<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n（暫時有5隻effect要比電 ）<br />\nSorry 199999<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/pokemon_2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/pokemon_2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7b44d15408d2b6818317ab21f81b8ed3b627765","tid":13754,"uid":26778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T08:32:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b9c743a69824cb09da2dd6f60ff122f6097281a","tid":13754,"uid":3615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T08:41:26.000Z","msg":"一分錢一分貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n買番d isolated source 囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e4db3e289273e8feb2f4ea2deac25e652da4a11","tid":13754,"uid":31632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T08:54:00.000Z","msg":"Voodoo lab 2plus 應該夠你而家或者將來增添pedal所用。佢行isolated output"},{"pid":"33731d2900052c80fc1269f0fbda0322d16f605a","tid":13754,"uid":26778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T09:44:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Voodoo lab 2plus 應該夠你而家或者將來增添pedal所用。佢行isolated output</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實我之前有用過mxr power supply 覺得幾好用 因為一來isolated 二來佢有個扭制可以調教比幾多電 <br />\n但前排冇啦啦死左 又冇keep單<br />\n巴打覺得我應該買返同一款mxr power supply 定 有其他性價比更加高既power supply?<br />\n岩岩上網睇過voodoo lab 2plus果款power supply 應該只可以選擇比9v /18v電？<br />\n求指教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77ccc289feac2d018882f45051e8fa3d682dbef3","tid":13754,"uid":26778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T13:21:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"372cc53c4970a1328b48b960801658148d8ce5cb","tid":13754,"uid":4383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T16:37:49.000Z","msg":"用左好耐one spot都唔覺有noise<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f1e91b0e1d19e297b909ccbb38bf310ea135ca8","tid":13754,"uid":31632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T16:45:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>Voodoo lab 2plus 應該夠你而家或者將來增添pedal所用。佢行isolated output</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實我之前有用過mxr power supply 覺得幾好用 因為一來isolated 二來佢有個扭制可以調教比幾多電 <br />\n但前排冇啦啦死左 又冇keep單<br />\n巴打覺得我應該買返同一款mxr power supply 定 有其他性價比更加高既power supply?<br />\n岩岩上網睇過voodoo lab 2plus果款power supply 應該只可以選擇比9v /18v電？<br />\n求指教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n2plus 佢有DIP switch 轉做12v <br />\n不過mA 就細啲<br />\n如果你覺得唔夠用既話咁可以考慮下1spot C12 pro <br />\n佢有9,12,18 v out  都係isolated<br />\n我唔考慮mxr 因為我覺得易壞"},{"pid":"37cc77bdeba8d9bf63453bc7a2fe6470a6649f16","tid":13754,"uid":31632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T16:47:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>用左好耐one spot都唔覺有noise<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁就要睇下你係咪用黎連住好多隻pedal <br />\n或者 係咪有用digital pedal<br />\n通常都係呢啲先多noise<br />\n就咁用analog pedal 冇乜事"},{"pid":"642a22bc4f014d60fdc2605da3edeae7bffa83f7","tid":13754,"uid":26778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T02:26:36.000Z","msg":"［quote]<br />\n<br />\n2plus 佢有DIP switch 轉做12v <br />\n不過mA 就細啲<br />\n如果你覺得唔夠用既話咁可以考慮下1spot C12 pro <br />\n佢有9,12,18 v out  都係isolated<br />\n我唔考慮mxr 因為我覺得易壞[/quote]<br />\n<br />\n唔該哂巴打 原來MXR易壞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42f09b779b87af263dfe59016af09dd7287c2cd6","tid":13754,"uid":31632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T06:09:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>［quote]<br />\n<br />\n2plus 佢有DIP switch 轉做12v <br />\n不過mA 就細啲<br />\n如果你覺得唔夠用既話咁可以考慮下1spot C12 pro <br />\n佢有9,12,18 v out  都係isolated<br />\n我唔考慮mxr 因為我覺得易壞<br />\n<br />\n唔該哂巴打 原來MXR易壞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我有隻mxr pedal 用左四年 第二年壞左一次<br />\n朋友有隻mxr pedal 用左三年 第二年壞左一次<br />\n唔明點解會咁易出事"},{"pid":"44a2409e8ae3154c5ef7b7c285a817ea5fb50e3a","tid":13754,"uid":26778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T07:04:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>［quote]<br />\n<br />\n2plus 佢有DIP switch 轉做12v <br />\n不過mA 就細啲<br />\n如果你覺得唔夠用既話咁可以考慮下1spot C12 pro <br />\n佢有9,12,18 v out  都係isolated<br />\n我唔考慮mxr 因為我覺得易壞<br />\n<br />\n唔該哂巴打 原來MXR易壞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我有隻mxr pedal 用左四年 第二年壞左一次<br />\n朋友有隻mxr pedal 用左三年 第二年壞左一次<br />\n唔明點解會咁易出事</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我果隻三個月就玩完 想問埋你講1spot果隻邊到有得買"},{"pid":"4fb5fe31fd65d0d353b202d548a446344a199797","tid":13754,"uid":3615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T07:36:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>［quote]<br />\n<br />\n2plus 佢有DIP switch 轉做12v <br />\n不過mA 就細啲<br />\n如果你覺得唔夠用既話咁可以考慮下1spot C12 pro <br />\n佢有9,12,18 v out  都係isolated<br />\n我唔考慮mxr 因為我覺得易壞<br />\n<br />\n唔該哂巴打 原來MXR易壞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我有隻mxr pedal 用左四年 第二年壞左一次<br />\n朋友有隻mxr pedal 用左三年 第二年壞左一次<br />\n唔明點解會咁易出事</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n睇番有d MXR pedal 既電路  佢用既IC 都有d歷史<br />\n同埋例如 10band eq 用料好過6band eq<br />\n6nand個個 望一望個電路真係DIY都靚過佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  一分錢一分貨啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  壞左個d可以拎比我試下有冇得救既<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/jj.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/jj.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過白色個隻bass compressor 真係幾靚仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}